steps.name: Verify redirection to the "Create new contact" form
Verify that the "Create new contact" form is visible
Fill in "First name" input field with: Domain
Fill in "Last name" input field with: Admin
Fill in "Address line1" input field with: 123 Street
Fill in "City" input field with: Paris
Click on "Country" dropdown and select a country: France
